<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Special+Gothic+Expanded+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logofinal.png">

    <style>
        body {
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2.5s forwards;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        .about {
            animation: slideInLeft 1s ease;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }
        .aboutpara {
            animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.4s backwards;
        }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        .profile-circle {
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,0,0,0.4);
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-top: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }
        .profile-circle img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .left-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .right-section {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding-left: 8%;
            margin-top: 8%;
        }
    </style>

    <title>about me.</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header', { activePage: 'about' }) %>
    <%- include('partials/videobg') %>

    <div class="profile-circle">
        <img src="/me.jpg" alt="Profile Picture">
    </div>

    <div class="about">
        about me.
    </div>

    <div class="aboutpara">
        hi, i’m shayne nathaniel, a year 2 ui/ux <br>design student at republic<br>polytechnic.
        i’ve always been<br>passionate about creativity since<br>young, using it as a way to express<br> myself and my thoughts.<br><br>

         for my ui design, i work mainly with<br> adobe photoshop and illustrator, alongside <br>apps like figma and canva, always looking<br>for new ways
        to blend style with<br>purpose.<br><br>

        outside of design, i love boxing and<br>cooking,
        they keep me sharp,<br>focused, and inspired.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
